14/02/2011
SARAJEVO, Bosnia and Herzegovina (BiH) -- Federation of BiH Minister for Veterans Issues Zahid Crnkic was seriously injured in a car accident near the town of Travnik late on Saturday (February 12th). Two others were also seriously injured, while a fourth person sustained minor injuries. Crnkic, 62, was transferred to a hospital in Sarajevo where he is listed in stable condition. (Srna, RTRS, BHRT, Radio Free Europe - 13/02/11)
